                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.00/1131.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port-au-Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 5, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Governor Fort and Mr. Smith arrived at Port-au-Prince at 11 this morning. Consul
                    Livingston arrived yesterday morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Blanchard</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
